comment: Monroe (MIL) makes incidental contact with Mills (SAS) that does not affect his SQBR.
Teletovic (MIL) and Aldridge (SAS) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Parker (MIL) makes marginal contact with Mills (SAS) on his move to the basket.
Snell (MIL) makes contact with Leonard (SAS) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Aldridge (SAS) cleanly dislodges the ball from Parker (MIL).
Antetokounmpo (MIL) jumps and lands prior to releasing the pass.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes contact with the ball after it has reached its apex and is on its downward flight toward the basket.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court (defensive goaltending) was upheld.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) spins away from Ginobili (SAS) on his move and the contact is marginal.
[Observable in enhanced video] Antetokounmpo (MIL) moves his pivot foot heel to toe.
